contentrichtext.text: '''[[Southport]]''' is a seaside town in Merseyside, England. '''Southport''' may also refer to: In '''Australia''' * [[Southport, Queensland]], a Gold Coast suburb * [[Electoral district of Southport]], Queensland, Australia * [[Southport, Northern Territory]], a suburb of Darwin * [[Southport Island]], Tasmania In '''Canada''' * [[Southport, Newfoundland and Labrador]] In the '''United States''' * [[Southport, Connecticut]], a distinct section of the town of Fairfield, Connecticut. * [[Southport, Florida]] * [[Southport, Indiana]] * [[Southport, Maine]] * [[Southport, New York]] ** [[Southport Correctional Facility]] * [[Southport, North Carolina]] * [[Kenosha, Wisconsin]] or Southport * [[Southport (CTA)]], a rapid-transit station in Chicago, Illinois ==See also== * [[South Port (disambiguation)]] {{geodis}}
